        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/9d8465/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-01-22T18:07:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>These old Drouhin wines can be very impressive. I drank through a case of 1978 Drouhin Chorey-les-Beaunes a few years ago that no one wanted at auction. Nearly every bottle was a true burgundy treasure.</p>",
